    "answerHTML": "\n<div class=\"faq-origin-tag\">Silent reason behind thousands of failed first stores</div>\n<p>You need to diagnose <em>where</em> in the funnel the drop-off happens before you can fix anything. This requires actual data, not guessing.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Check Shopify Analytics → Conversion Funnel:</strong> Sessions → Product page views → Add to cart → Checkout started → Purchased. Find the biggest drop-off percentage between each step.</li>\n<div class=\"inline-tools-label\">CRO Tools</div>\n<div class=\"inline-tools-grid\">\n<a class=\"itkc\" href=\"https://hotjar.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"itkc-logo\"><img alt=\"Hotjar\" onerror=\"this.parentNode.innerHTML='🔥'\" src=\"/images/hotjar.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div>\n<div class=\"itkc-info\"><div class=\"itkc-name\">Hotjar</div><div class=\"itkc-desc\">Heatmaps &amp; session recordings — see drop-offs visually</div></div>\n<span class=\"itkc-cta\">Try Free</span>\n</a>\n<a class=\"itkc\" href=\"https://intelligems.io\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"itkc-logo\"><img alt=\"Intelligems\" onerror=\"this.parentNode.innerHTML='🧪'\" src=\"/images/intelligems.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div>\n<div class=\"itkc-info\"><div class=\"itkc-name\">Intelligems</div><div class=\"itkc-desc\">A/B test pricing on Shopify to find the optimal price</div></div>\n<span class=\"itkc-cta\">Try Free</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n<li><strong>Sessions → Product page view below 50%:</strong> Traffic is landing somewhere other than your product page. Check your ad destination URL.</li>\n<li><strong>Product page view → ATC below 5%:</strong> Your product page isn't convincing. Most common issues: weak headline, no social proof above the fold, price shock, no clear value proposition in the first screen.</li>\n<li><strong>ATC → Checkout below 60%:</strong> Unexpected costs at cart. Hidden shipping fee, no PayPal, trust issues.</li>\n<li><strong>Checkout started → Purchased below 50%:</strong> Payment friction. Card form trust issues, confusing checkout flow, slow load time on mobile.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Each stage has a specific fix. Don't guess — find the actual drop-off point first, then apply the fix for that specific layer.</p>\n",
    "answerText": "You need to diagnose where in the funnel the drop-off happens before you can fix anything. This requires actual data, not guessing. Check Shopify Analytics → Conversion Funnel: Sessions → Product page views → Add to cart → Checkout started → Purchased. Find the biggest drop-off percentage between each step. CRO Tools HotjarHeatmaps & session recordings — see drop-offs visually Try Free IntelligemsA/B test pricing on Shopify to find the optimal price Try Free Sessions → Product page view below 50%: Traffic is landing somewhere other than your product page. Check your ad destination URL. Product page view → ATC below 5%: Your product page isn't convincing. Most common issues: weak headline, no social proof above the fold, price shock, no clear value proposition in the first screen. ATC → Checkout below 60%: Unexpected costs at cart. Hidden shipping fee, no PayPal, trust issues. Checkout started → Purchased below 50%: Payment friction. Card form trust issues, confusing checkout flow, slow load time on mobile. Each stage has a specific fix. Don't guess — find the actual drop-off point first, then apply the fix for that specific layer.",
