    "answerText": "For testing phase: default Dawn theme. Stop optimizing the container. Dawn is fast, mobile-responsive, and converts well enough to validate products. No page builder required until you have a winning product that justifies CRO investment. GemPages and Replo are excellent tools — for specific use cases. They shine when you need custom landing pages for higher-ticket products, advertorial funnels, or when you're iterating rapidly on a proven winner and need A/B testing capability. They are overkill for testing phase. The operators who spend a week building a \"perfect\" GemPages store before they've validated a single product are procrastinating. A beautiful store with no validated product is an expensive hobby. A functional Dawn store with a winning angle is a business. Shopify Page Builders (For Scale Phase) GemPages100+ CRO-optimised templates — best for non-technical ops Get GemPages ReploNative Shopify landing pages used by $1M+ brands Try Replo Zipify PagesBuilt by 7-figure operators for paid traffic funnels Get Zipify Tactical FixLaunch with Dawn. Focus on: (1) fast load time, (2) clear value proposition above the fold, (3) social proof (reviews), (4) trust signals near buy button, (5) all payment methods active. That's the entire CRO checklist for a testing store. Only invest in a page builder after you have a product converting above break-even ROAS.",
